Suspected killer herdsmen in fake military and Customs uniforms have reportedly invaded Igangan in Ibarapa area of Oyo State, killing residents. Though hunters and Amotekun personnel were said to have risen up to repel them, an Amotekun commandant in the area was said to have been killed in the attack. The Nation gathered the attack on Friday night threw the sleepy town into disarray. Details shortlyâ€¦